# Apple Agentic Swift 2026

Read `AGENTS.md`. Enforce the rules in `rules/`.

Key constraints:

- Local-first AI with Foundation Models where available.
- Typed guided generation and bounded tools.
- App Intents/AppEntity for system integration.
- Fruta-inspired shared SwiftUI codebase for app + widget + App Clip + intents.
- Swift 6-ready concurrency and data-race safety.
- Privacy manifest/App Review updates for data-flow changes.
- Use hooks and automations from `.agent/`, `.claude/`, `scripts/`, and `automations/`.
